{"tid":142083,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英足總擬引入重播技術\t最快下季社區盾使用","createTime":"2017-03-03T12:39:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T00:10:42.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a8c1d5f7fdf565bb973ec6a3f73dc148f1a3d739","tid":142083,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:39:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>英足總擬引入重播技術\t最快下季社區盾使用</strong><br />\n<br />\n2017-03-03 20:34:50 HKT  <br />\n         <br />\n修咸頓早前在英格蘭聯賽盃決賽中慘食詐胡，遭球證錯判越位而失去先開紀錄的機會。<br />\n<br />\n以電視重播協助執法，似乎已經係大勢所趨，國際足協上年12月嘅世界冠軍球會盃，就係首個用電視重播協助執法嘅大賽，如果技術成熟，2018年世界盃有機會全面推行。據報英格蘭足總已經希望將重播技術引入本土賽事，而且研究先喺社區盾、英足盃等賽事先試行，下季社區盾好大機會喺英格蘭首個用呢個技術嘅盃賽。"},{"pid":"f543d524933c6e35fe7889da40879c8836984bb4","tid":142083,"uid":30751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:45:00.000Z","msg":"咁可唔可以重賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ed6108abb4ddf3b05e91604636aee4182a690c","tid":142083,"uid":43328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T18:05:58.000Z","msg":"迫害阿仙奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b508aefca97616c7ef99a70231a16392e7bc3442","tid":142083,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T18:13:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>迫害阿仙奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39051b4ffa932adefb79fb46e958a3979d5aef7b","tid":142083,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T18:17:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>迫害阿仙奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68134f90779907f060827974513813196443f7de","tid":142083,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,